commit.message:
Merge pull request #19 from andregumieri/develop

First delivery
Fix the manifest to runs on yelp.ca and yelp.com.br
Runs the extension only inside /biz/* pages
Fix #17: Hide right button when finished
Fixes #5 #16: Erros message for no videos and API errors
Fix #8: Put all the icons on manifest
Fix #2: Avoids nav button to pass the end of strip

Improve the 'isARestaurantPage' condition

Instead of just search for the first occurence of the word restaurant
in the breadcrumb, now I look on all tags to see if any of them is
restaurant. Some pages has another tag in the first occurrence but
it doesn't mean it shouldn't be treated as a restaurant.

Sample http://www.yelp.com/biz/dangerous-dans-diner-toronto
WIP: DOM injection in the restaurant page
Views folder and views task on gulp
